27:46.231 --> 27:46.664
PARTICULARLY THE "SEND A

27:46.731 --> 27:47.332
SENSIBLE PERSON" POINT.

27:47.399 --> 27:48.333
BECAUSE WHEN YOU'RE DEALING WITH

27:48.400 --> 27:49.834
THE ROYAL FAMILY, IT'S WORTH

27:49.901 --> 27:50.769
REMEMBER THAT UNLESS YOU

27:50.835 --> 27:52.003
