DIG THAT CRAZY RHYTHM!

27:57.442 --> 28:02.547
>> John: EXACTLY.

28:02.614 --> 28:05.083
AND NOBODY WANTS THAT, NOBODY!

28:05.150 --> 28:05.650
YOU CAN'T SAY YOU'RE JUST A

28:05.717 --> 28:06.084
SYMBOL AND BEAR NO

28:06.151 --> 28:06.851
RESPONSIBILITY FOR HOW THE

28:06.918 --> 28:08.286
INSTITUTIONS YOU'RE THE HEAD OF

28:08.353 --> 28:09.387
BEHAVE.

28:09.454 --> 28:10.822
TAKE THE CHURCH OF ENGLAND, OF

28:10.889 --> 28:12.090
WHICH THE MONARCH IS THE HEAD.

28:12.157 --> 28:13.525
IN CANADA, IT PLAYED A ROLE IN

28:13.591 --> 28:14.592
THEIR SYSTEM OF RESIDENTIAL

28:14.659 --> 28:16.227
SCHOOLS FOR INDIGENOUS CHILDREN,

28:16.294 --> 28:17.695
WHO WERE FORCIBLY SEPARATED FROM

28:17.762 --> 28:19.664
THEIR FAMILIES AND SENT TO

28:19.731 --> 28:20.832
GOVERNMENT-FUNDED, CHURCH-RUN

28:20.899 --> 28:23.334
BOARDING SCHOOLS IN ATTEMPT TO

28:23.401 --> 28:23.701
ASSIMILATE THEM.

28:23.768 --> 28:24.836
HORRIFIC ABUSES HAPPENED IN

28:24.903 --> 28:25.970
THOSE SCHOOLS.

28:26.037 --> 28:27.705
AND WHILE THEY WERE LARGELY RUN

28:27.772 --> 28:28.907
BY THE CATHOLIC CHURCH, THE

28:28.973 --> 28:30.275
CHURCH OF ENGLAND OPERATED

28:30.341 --> 28:31.709
APPROXIMATELY THREE DOZEN OF

28:31.776 --> 28:33.678
THEM, GIVING UP CONTROL OF THE

28:33.745 --> 28:36.114
LAST ONE IN 1969, WHICH IS

28:36.181 --> 28:37.282
PRETTY FUCKING RECENT.

28:37.348 --> 28:38.516
EARLIER THIS YEAR, CHARLES

28:38.583 --> 28:39.818
VISITED CANADA AND MADE A POINT

28:39.884 --> 28:41.319
OF SHOWING UP AT A GARDEN THAT

28:41.386 --> 28:42.454
PAID TRIBUTE TO THE VICTIMS OF

28:42.520 --> 28:43.321
THOSE SCHOOLS.

28:43.388 --> 28:45.323
BUT WHEN IT CAME TO SHOWING

28:45.390 --> 28:46.157
REMORSE FOR WHAT HAD HAPPENED,

28:46.224 --> 28:46.958
THAT SEEMED TO BE OFF THE TABLE.

28:47.025 --> 28:48.726
BECAUSE JUST LISTEN TO ONE

28:48.793 --> 28:50.028
INDIGENOUS LEADER WHO BRIEFLY

28:50.095 --> 28:51.596
