29:00.872 --> 29:02.574
THE PRINCE, WHILE LEADING THIS

29:02.640 --> 29:04.075
COUNTRY, HE SHOULD APOLOGIZE TO

29:04.142 --> 29:06.578
THE ABORIGINAL PEOPLE FOR THIS

29:06.644 --> 29:08.046
TRAUMA THAT WE'VE GONE THROUGH

29:08.113 --> 29:09.547
FOR 500 YEARS.

29:09.614 --> 29:10.281
>> John: WOW.

29:10.348 --> 29:12.283
"I HOPE WE WEREN'T TOO BAD ON

29:12.350 --> 29:13.651
YOU," HE SAID, BEFORE WALKING

29:13.718 --> 29:14.185
