29:14.252 --> 29:16.621
WHICH I KNOW SEEMS BAD, BUT AS A

29:16.688 --> 29:21.726
SYMBOL OF BRITAIN, IT'S PRETTY

29:21.793 --> 29:22.794
ON-BRAND HONESTLY.

29:22.861 --> 29:32.203
"YOU KEEP CALM.

29:32.270 --> 29:33.238
AND IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME, I'LL

29:33.304 --> 29:33.505
CARRY ON."

29:33.571 --> 29:34.005
AND LOOK, I KNOW, ACROSS

29:34.072 --> 29:34.606
COMMONWEALTH COUNTRIES, THERE

29:34.672 --> 29:35.273
ARE A RANGE OF VIEWS, ESPECIALLY

29:35.340 --> 29:35.874
AMONG THE OLDER GENERATION --

29:35.940 --> 29:36.474
AS, INCREDIBLY, EVEN SOME WHO

29:36.541 --> 29:37.108
SUFFERED UNDER BRITISH RULE CAN

29:37.175 --> 29:37.775
FEEL STRONG AFFECTION FOR THE

29:37.842 --> 29:38.443
QUEEN PERSONALLY, EVEN IF THEY

29:38.510 --> 29:39.344
DIDN'T LOVE WHAT SHE

29:39.410 --> 29:39.711
REPRESENTED.

29:39.777 --> 29:40.879
AND SOME ARGUE, "IF THE ROYAL

29:40.945 --> 29:42.313
FAMILY'S JUST CEREMONIAL NOW,

29:42.380 --> 29:43.681
WHERE'S THE REAL HARM?"

29:43.748 --> 29:45.583
BUT THE CEREMONIAL CAN STILL

29:45.650 --> 29:46.985
HAVE THE POWER TO INFURIATE.

29:47.051 --> 29:47.952
AND TO SEE THAT, LET'S GO BACK

29:48.019 --> 29:49.487
TO AUSTRALIA.

29:49.554 --> 29:50.889
BECAUSE SHORTLY BEFORE THE QUEEN

29:50.955 --> 29:52.090
DIED, LIDIA THORPE, AN

29:52.157 --> 29:53.758
INDIGENOUS AUSTRALIAN SENATOR

29:53.825 --> 29:55.293
WAS TAKING THE OATH OF OFFICE,

29:55.360 --> 29:56.528
WHICH REQUIRED HER TO SWEAR

29:56.594 --> 29:57.529
ALLEGIANCE TO THE QUEEN.

29:57.595 --> 29:59.497
SOMETHING SHE UNDERSTANDABLY HAD

29:59.564 --> 30:01.032
A BIT OF A PROBLEM WITH, SO THIS

30:01.099 --> 30:01.833
IS WHAT SHE DID.

30:01.900 --> 30:05.270
>> PLEASE RECITE THE AFFIRMATION

30:05.336 --> 30:08.840
ON THE CARD HANDED TO YOU.

30:08.907 --> 30:09.908
>> I, SOVEREIGN LIDIA THORPE, DO

30:09.974 --> 30:13.878
SOLEMNLY AND SINCERELY AFFIRM

30:13.945 --> 30:15.513
AND DECLARE THAT I WILL BE

30:15.580 --> 30:18.316
FAITHFUL, AND I BEAR TRUE

30:18.383 --> 30:21.452
ALLEGIANCE TO THE COLONIZING HER

30:21.519 --> 30:22.020
MAJESTY QUEEN ELIZABETH II.

30:22.086 --> 30:22.954
>> SENATOR THORPE -- SENATOR

30:23.021 --> 30:24.389
THORPE, YOU ARE REQUIRED TO

30:24.455 --> 30:26.691
RECITE THE OATH AS PRINTED ON

30:26.758 --> 30:27.725
THE CARD.

30:27.792 --> 30:28.726
>> John: YEAH, THEY ACTUALLY

30:28.793 --> 30:30.361
FORCED HER TO READ WHAT WAS

30:30.428 --> 30:35.333
PRINTED ON THE CARD, VERBATIM.

30:35.400 --> 30:37.335
SO SHE DID THAT, BUT CREDIT TO

30:37.402 --> 30:38.870
HER -- BECAUSE SHE THEN EMPLOYED

30:38.937 --> 30:39.604
A TONE OF VOICE THAT DID A "LOT"

30:39.671 --> 30:40.271
OF HEAVY LIFTING.

30:40.338 --> 30:40.905
>> I, LIDIA THORPE, DO SOLEMNLY

30:40.972 --> 30:44.309
AND SINCERELY AFFIRM AND DECLARE

30:44.375 --> 30:46.778
THAT I WILL BE FAITHFUL AND BEAR

30:46.844 --> 30:53.117
TRUE ALLEGIANCE TO HER MAJESTY

30:53.184 --> 30:54.152
QUEEN ELIZABETH II, HER HEIRS,

30:54.219 --> 31:00.058
AND SUCCESSORS ACCORDING TO LAW.

31:00.124 --> 31:01.459
>> John: OKAY, I HATE THAT SHE

31:01.526 --> 31:02.360
WAS FORCED TO DO THAT, BUT I

31:02.427 --> 31:04.229
ABSOLUTELY LOVE THE WAY SHE WAS

31:04.295 --> 31:05.964
ABLE TO MAKE A PLEDGE TO A FANCY

31:06.030 --> 31:06.564
OLD LADY ON THE OTHER SIDE OF

31:06.631 --> 31:09.100
THE WORLD SOUND EXACTLY AS

31:09.167 --> 31:11.236
STUPID AS IT FUCKING IS.

31:11.302 --> 31:12.870
AND LOOK, TO GO BY RECENT POLLS,

31:12.937 --> 31:13.871
AUSTRALIA -- LIKE THE UK --

31:13.938 --> 31:15.473
SEEMS UNLIKELY TO LET GO OF THE

31:15.540 --> 31:17.375
MONARCHY ANYTIME SOON.

31:17.442 --> 31:19.611
BUT OTHER COMMONWEALTH COUNTRIES

31:19.677 --> 31:21.179
ARE ALREADY PREPARING TO DO SO.

31:21.246 --> 31:22.847
LAST YEAR, BARBADOS REMOVED THE

31:22.914 --> 31:23.848
QUEEN AS HEAD OF STATE.

31:23.915 --> 31:25.216
JAMAICA IS LOOKING TO HAVE A

31:25.283 --> 31:26.551
REFERENDUM TO DO THE SAME WITHIN

31:26.618 --> 31:27.552
THE NEXT THREE YEARS, WITH ONE

31:27.619 --> 31:29.354
POLL SHOWING A MAJORITY SUPPORTS

31:29.420 --> 31:31.189
IT.

31:31.256 --> 31:32.557
AND ANTIGUA AND BARBUDA, GRENADA

31:32.624 --> 31:33.191
AND BELIZE SEEM TO BE MOVING IN

31:33.258 --> 31:35.193
THE SAME DIRECTION.

31:35.260 --> 31:35.994
AND WHILE THE ROYAL FAMILY'S

31:36.060 --> 31:37.629
SAID THESE COUNTRIES ARE FREE TO

31:37.695 --> 31:38.630
LEAVE IF THEY SO CHOOSE, THEY

31:38.696 --> 31:40.732
ALSO REFUSE TO RECKON WITH WHY

31:40.798 --> 31:42.033
THEY MIGHT WANT TO DO THAT IN

31:42.100 --> 31:43.134
THE FIRST PLACE.

31:43.201 --> 31:44.802
INSTEAD, THEY'VE CONTINUED

31:44.869 --> 31:45.903
WORKING HARD TO BE PERCEIVED AS

31:45.970 --> 31:47.138
A MERE "SYMBOL," WHILE NEVER

31:47.205 --> 31:49.907
TAKING RESPONSIBILITY FOR WHAT

31:49.974 --> 31:50.708
THAT SYMBOL EXCUSED -- ALL WHILE

31:50.775 --> 31:51.876
IGNORING CALLS FOR TRUE

31:51.943 --> 31:53.845
APOLOGIES AND REPARATIONS TO

31:53.911 --> 31:55.346
THOSE WHO SUFFERED TREMENDOUSLY

31:55.413 --> 31:57.382
BECAUSE OF WHAT WAS DONE IN

31:57.448 --> 31:58.583
THEIR NAME.

31:58.650 --> 32:00.418
AND LOOK, YOU DON'T HAVE TO HATE

32:00.485 --> 32:02.453
THE ROYAL FAMILY PERSONALLY.

