32:14.132 --> 32:15.566
TO EXPECT SIGNIFICANTLY MORE

32:15.633 --> 32:16.868
FROM THEM.

32:16.934 --> 32:17.602
BECAUSE RIGHT NOW, FAR TOO

32:17.669 --> 32:25.176
OFTEN, THEY HIDE BEHIND THE

32:25.243 --> 32:25.677
SHIELD OF POLITENESS AND

32:25.743 --> 32:26.210
MANNERS, WHICH FREQUENTLY

32:26.277 --> 32:26.811
