32:26.878 --> 32:27.378
WHO MIGHT CRITICIZE THEM, OR

32:27.445 --> 32:27.845
WHAT THEY STAND FOR.

32:27.912 --> 32:28.446
WILL THIS SEGMENT EVEN AIR ON

32:28.513 --> 32:30.348
SKY IN BRITAIN?

