32:36.721 --> 32:37.488
DISRESPECTFUL, THEY MIGHT WANT

32:37.555 --> 32:39.957
TO THINK ABOUT WHY.

32:40.024 --> 32:41.059
WHY THEY, AND EVERYONE ELSE, ARE

32:41.125 --> 32:42.593
WORKING SO HARD NOT TO OFFEND A

32:42.660 --> 32:44.128
FAMILY WHOSE NAME WAS BRANDED

32:44.195 --> 32:47.532
INTO PEOPLE'S SKIN, AND WHO SIT

32:47.598 --> 32:48.833
ATOP A PILE OF STOLEN WEALTH,

32:48.900 --> 32:50.134
WEARING CROWNS ADORNED WITH

32:50.201 --> 32:51.536
OTHER COUNTRIES' TREASURES.

32:51.602 --> 32:56.207
